headline: BlackRock Sustainable Advantage Large Cap Core Fund Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: BlackRock Sustainable Advantage Large Cap Core Fund posted returns of 1.60% (Institutional shares) and 1.57% (Investor A shares, without sales charge) for the fourth quarter of 2024.
